---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Kangaroo Point Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Kangaroo Point Brisbane. Clifftop riverside suburb with stunning city views and strong demand. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Kangaroo Point Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Kangaroo Point Brisbane, serving the riverside inner city.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/kangaroo-point",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Kangaroo Point", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/kangaroo-point" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the median house price in Kangaroo Point?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Kangaroo Point's median sits at approximately $1.5 million as of early 2026, though the market here spans affordable apartments through to premium clifftop residences. The suburb's dramatic position above the river and proximity to the CBD create a wide price range across different property types." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to sell a property in Kangaroo Point?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Well-priced Kangaroo Point properties typically sell within 28 to 42 days. Clifftop homes and properties with city and river views tend to attract faster and more competitive buyer interest than standard mid-rise apartments in the suburb." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What makes Kangaroo Point unique?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Kangaroo Point sits on a dramatic sandstone cliff above the Brisbane River, offering city skyline views that few suburbs can match at this proximity to the CBD. The Story Bridge, riverside parklands and the Captain Burke Park walkway create a lifestyle that is genuinely distinctive within Brisbane's inner suburbs." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Kangaroo Point a good suburb to invest in?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Kangaroo Point's inner-city location, tourist appeal and consistent rental demand from professionals and short-stay tenants support strong yields. The suburb's proximity to the Gabba and planned Olympics infrastructure investment has also maintained investor interest in the area." }
    }
  ]
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Kangaroo Point</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Kangaroo Point.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Kangaroo Point and Brisbane's riverside inner city.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/appraisal" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's Your Property Worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Clifftop living with some of Brisbane's best views.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Kangaroo Point offers a rare combination of city proximity, riverside access and dramatic elevated views. It attracts a mix of owner-occupiers drawn to lifestyle and investors seeking strong rental demand from professionals working in the CBD.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand what makes properties in Kangaroo Point stand out and how to position them to attract the most competitive buyers. Whether apartment or house, the right campaign here can deliver exceptional results.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The famous Kangaroo Point cliffs draw visitors daily and give the suburb a landmark identity that few Brisbane addresses can claim. Story Bridge at the northern tip frames city views that are genuinely among the best in Brisbane and underpin premium values for apartments with north-facing outlooks. Main Street's restaurant and cafe strip has matured significantly, offering residents a walkable dining precinct that further removes any need to own a car. CBD walkability across the Captain Burke Park footbridge means Kangaroo Point regularly tops buyer preference surveys for inner-city professionals, keeping rental yields strong and owner-occupier competition fierce.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Kangaroo Point Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Riverside Inner City</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Premium Views</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong rental demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/east-brisbane" style="color:#c4912a;">East Brisbane</a>, <a href="/suburbs/new-farm" style="color:#c4912a;">New Farm</a>, <a href="/suburbs/woolloongabba" style="color:#c4912a;">Woolloongabba</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION: FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Kangaroo Point.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Kangaroo Point?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kangaroo Point's median sits at approximately $1.5 million as of early 2026, though the market here spans affordable apartments through to premium clifftop residences. The suburb's dramatic position above the river and proximity to the CBD create a wide price range across different property types.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a property in Kangaroo Point?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Kangaroo Point properties typically sell within 28 to 42 days. Clifftop homes and properties with city and river views tend to attract faster and more competitive buyer interest than standard mid-rise apartments in the suburb.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What makes Kangaroo Point unique?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kangaroo Point sits on a dramatic sandstone cliff above the Brisbane River, offering city skyline views that few suburbs can match at this proximity to the CBD. The Story Bridge, riverside parklands and the Captain Burke Park walkway create a lifestyle that is genuinely distinctive within Brisbane's inner suburbs.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Kangaroo Point a good suburb to invest in?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Kangaroo Point's inner-city location, tourist appeal and consistent rental demand from professionals and short-stay tenants support strong yields. The suburb's proximity to the Gabba and planned Olympics infrastructure investment has also maintained investor interest in the area.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

